BugReportMemento - Class in bugtrap03.bugdomain.bugreport
This class is the Memento of BugReport, this means it is a snapshot of the state of a BugReport.
Caution: Due to time/effort balancing this currently is not a fully functional Memento in the way that it is designed to fit with the undo operations.
